4. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper's focus on optimizing the sum of substream outage capacities under a given sum power constraint can be related to networking and internet architecture. 
5. cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) - The paper's use of optimal power allocation and cutoff value calculation can be related to game theory concepts.
